            <title>[SOLR-15058] Solr can not get correct hostname when hostname contain &apos;_&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15058</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Utils.getBaseUrlForNodeName split the nodename by the first &apos;_&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In ZK, Solr add &apos;_solr&apos; to the end of the hostname&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;so there should split by the last &apos;_&apos;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
